These patches apply on top of XenServer 7.0 sources:

  https://github.com/xenserver/xen-4.5
  https://github.com/xenserver/xen-4.5.pg

Please see the xen source documentation on how to build it and apply
patches on top of the source tree.

Quick HOWTO:
  1. clone the xen-4.5 repository to /some/path/xen-4.5/
  2. clone hvi-4.5 patch queue repository to /some/path/xen-4.5/.git/patches/
  3. cd /some/path/xen-4.5 and then do a `guilt push -a` to apply the patches
